description:
Decrypt files encrypted by Cryptainer and SecureIT 2000

DeCypherIT is a freeware utility, part of the award winning suite of Products from CypherixÂ®. This utility allows you to decrypt encrypted files generated by Cryptainer and SecureIT 2000.
It is very simple to use. Simply point/locate the encrypted file that has been sent to you. Enter the password. That's it!
